column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.subclass, s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.zwarning FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.class=&&&  AND s.zwarning=#  AND (s.subclass LIKE &&& OR s.subclass LIKE &&&)
